rack record our track record includes  ipos recently twilio mindbody flex pharma shopify box u and wix joined the ranks of bvp funded public companies yelp linkedin eloqua criteo and cornerstone on demand  along the way we’ve seen a number of our most exciting and innovative startups become part of something larger recent examples include periscope which sold to twitter before they launched twitch which was acquired by amazon for b and skybox imaging which was bought by google in  marking the first—and largest acquisition to date—in the new race for space   we invest wherever great companies are being built from seven offices around the world silicon valley middlefield road suite menlo park ca   san francisco brannan st suite san francisco ca  westchester palmer avenue suite larchmont ny   new york city madison avenue suite new york  ny  boston broadway nd floorcambridge ma  israel  hasadnaot streetseaview building a th floorherzliya pituachisrael   india vittal mallya road nd floorbangalore   india by the numbers  ipos b current fund  investment professionals business plans businessplansbvpcom press inquiries pressbvpcom website comments webmasterbvpcom download brand assets bessemer securities corporation credit report products contacts florida search bessemer securities corporation company number  status active fei number  company type foreign for profit home state de last activity date  date of incorporation  principal address  fifth ave new york ny  mailing address  fifth ave new york ny  bessemer securities corporation principals president chairman e o lindsay robert d address  fifth ave new york ny  secretary vice president president chairman markowitz howard address  fifth ave new york ny  treasurer secretary vice president president macdonald john g address  fifth ave th fl new york ny  last annual reports       registered agent agent name corporation service company c agent address  hays street tallahassee fl  bessemer securities corporation events  amendm